  "detailed_description": "When a quiet family of rabbits is abducted by evil space foxes, only a brave rabbit can help.<br>Join in an adventure with hidden traps, escape from a fireball rains, drive a scooter, face a giant fox robot, explore caves, fly in a rocket and defeat the evil boss to bring the bunnies home!<br><br>Rambunny is a 2D platform game with moderate difficulty, containing 10 stages divided into small dungeons.<br><br><strong>Want More!?</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Infinite lives<br></li><li>Cutscenes<br></li><li>Easter Eggs<br></li><li>Cute Bunnies<br></li><li>Hidden Traps<br></li><li>Pixel Art<br></li><li>Funny Hero<br></li><li>Nonsense plot<br></li><li>Scooter and Rocket Stage<br></li><li>Steam Achievements<br></li><li>Evil Galactic Boss<br></li><li>Own Language in Balloons<br></li><li>Cheap Game</li></ul>",
